{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Public Inquiry into Unfair Trading Practices of Holiday Caravan Park Owners",
        "additional_details": "An investigation is needed to establish if there are systemic unlawful trading practices by Holiday Caravan Park companies across the UK. We believe there is overwhelming evidence of detriment to 1000s of consumers, many of whom face loss of their homes. An Inquiry followed by positive interventions would be an efficient and effective way of resolving a national crisis for consumers.",
        "background": "The Government should launch an inquiry into the terms of standard consumer contracts issued by trade members of the NCC and BH&HPA, to establish if the terms and practices are unfair for the purposes of the CRA 2015 and if the practices breach the Unfair Trading Regs 2008.",
